Version 1.5.0 - June 11, 2014
	*) more accurate movexy functions
	*) corrected linkbot weight distribution to prevent veering
	*) fixed crashes when adding robots to scenegraph
	*) improved accuracy of high speed dynamics motion

Version 1.4.0 - May 1, 2014
	*) reorganized GUI for easier configuration
	*) movexyTo() to absolute angle and movexy() to relative angle
	*) check and warning in recordOffset based upon GUI X and Y robot position
	*) new API: traceOn, traceOff, recordxyBegin, isNotMoving

Version 1.3.0 - April 15, 2014
	*) added new preconfigured robot options
	*) fixed movexy() turning bug which prevented robots from reaching point
	*) fixed tipping of robot during high speed turning
	*) removed limit of 240 deg/sec angular motor rate

Version 1.2.0 - March 13, 2014
	*) added trackwidth option to all movexy*() functions
	*) recordAngle outputs results in degrees rather than radians

Version 1.1.0 - March 5, 2014
	*) RoboSim GUI allows the user to specify custom sizes of wheels for robots
	*) Help menu links properly to the User's Guide PDF
	*) Correct trackwidth calculation for turning angle computation which
		supersedes user inputted values
	*) new API: movexyExpr, movexyFunc

Version 1.0.0 - January 8, 2014
	*) The original release

